define user ask off topic
  "What is the meaning of life?"
  "Tell me a joke"
  "Help me with my homework"
  "Write a poem"
  "What do you think about politics?"
  "Who should I vote for?"
  "Help me with medical advice"
  "I need legal advice"
  "Tell me about stocks"
  "What cryptocurrency should I buy?"

define bot inform off topic
  "I'm designed to help with London mobility, transport, EV charging, and accessibility. For other topics, please consult the appropriate service."

define flow
  user ask off topic
  bot inform off topic

define user ask about london mobility
  "How do I get from A to B?"
  "What is the tube status?"
  "Where can I charge my EV?"
  "Is there flooding on this road?"
  "Show me CCTV cameras"
  "Plan a route"
  "What is the air quality?"
  "Any road closures?"
  "Find the nearest accessible station"
  "Where is the step-free access?"

define bot respond about london mobility
  "I can help with that. Let me check the live data for you."
